title: Are the results exactly the same on Mac and on Ubuntu?
body_html:
Here is what I am testing:
https://github.com/devnag/pytorch-generative-adversarial-networks
A GAN example.

I found that for the same code, the results are different when running on Mac (Python 3.6) and on Ubuntu (Python 2.7). All Pytorch is the latest release version.
Plus, on Ubuntu, the example have a good result but on Mac, unfortunately, in most cases, the result is not well enough.

Is that because Python version?
